headline: GEHC Launches AI-Powered Vivid Pioneer Cardiac Ultrasound System
summary: GE HealthCare's Vivid Pioneer, cleared by CE Mark and FDA, brings AI-powered speed, precision and efficiency to cardiac imaging.
